{"tid":254222,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[正顎手術］召集所有倒及的巴絲打","createTime":"2017-05-23T04:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T19:10:33.000Z","uid":118416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"254ce87cc34d1523e7667cc1ab7d05f2f8cfb45d","tid":254222,"uid":118416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"之前consult左林醫生，佢話我個case要做手術先可以改善到，所以refer左我去睇一個專科。<br />\n<br />\n今日睇左專科，話如果私家做的話就大概要三十萬到，屋企真係負擔唔到。佢話排公立就6-7年先有得開始cool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔想成三十幾先開始搞<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家係咪真係要排咁耐，睇之前d巴絲打一兩年就有得開始做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問你地個時係點搞<br />\n<br />\n求介紹好的專科醫生轉介睇公立可以快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a6757ce5cdc879340851fca5ff4d84b7d2c94c","tid":254222,"uid":34222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:55:53.000Z","msg":"我黎緊7月係ppdh做<br />\n<br />\n大概都係2年前度睇<br />\n<br />\ncool左牙年半度<br />\n<br />\n由yr1 搞到而家升yr3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec30a64f3474c9c8773dcb9797dc734de57e4b2e","tid":254222,"uid":118416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我黎緊7月係ppdh做<br />\n<br />\n大概都係2年前度睇<br />\n<br />\ncool左牙年半度<br />\n<br />\n由yr1 搞到而家升yr3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係好識 ppd係咪姐係直接凌晨5，6點鐘去佢門口排隊攞籌等見醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbb47abb69370bd8a025439435d07f976545c8b","tid":254222,"uid":4219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:09:19.000Z","msg":"係真係要排咁耐 我個妹10歲排到18先有得做<br />\nbtw樓豬男定女？女仔就貪靚當整下容都得既 <br />\n不過男既唔做好過做 我個妹上